&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt; &lt;img width=&quot;500&quot; src=&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/collanotewiki/collanotewiki.github.io/main/images/FAQimage/import-pdf.JPEG&quot; alt=&quot;picture import-PDF&quot; /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

